(
<bibRefCitation author="Aiton, W." box="[144,331,2040,2067]" pageId="1" pageNumber="106" refId="ref2598" refString="Aiton, W. (1789) Hortus Kewensis, vol. 1. Printed for George Nicol, Bookseller to his Majesty, London, 496 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 4504" type="book" year="1789">Aiton 1789: 286</bibRefCitation>
) Webb
</taxonomicName>
(in 
<bibRefCitation author="Hooker, W. J." box="[454,661,2040,2066]" pageId="1" pageNumber="106" refId="ref3246" refString="Hooker, W. J. (1849) Niger flora. H. Bailliere, London, 587 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 594" type="book" year="1849">Hooker 1849: 104</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName authority="Poiret" authorityName="Poiret" box="[681,871,2040,2066]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Polycarpaea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="1" pageNumber="106" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="latifolia">
<emphasis box="[681,798,2040,2066]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="106">P. latifolia</emphasis>
Poiret
</taxonomicName>
(in 
<bibRefCitation author="Lamarck, J. &amp; Poiret, J. L. M." box="[916,1242,2040,2066]" pageId="1" pageNumber="106" refId="ref3799" refString="Lamarck, J. &amp; Poiret, J. L. M. (1816) Encyclopeidie meithodique. Botanique. Supplement, Tome 4. Madame veuve Agasse imprimeurlibraire, Paris, 731 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 826" type="book" year="1816">Lamarck &amp; Poiret 1816: 473</bibRefCitation>
), and 
<taxonomicName authority="Poiret ex Steudel" authorityName="Steudel" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Polycarpaea" kingdom="Plantae" lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="107" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="1" pageNumber="106" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="divaricata">
<emphasis box="[1309,1451,2040,2066]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="106">P. divaricata</emphasis>
Poiret ex Steudel
</taxonomicName>
(in 
<bibRefCitation author="Steudel, E. T." box="[367,573,158,185]" pageId="2" pageNumber="107" refId="ref4246" refString="Steudel, E. T. (1841) Nomenclator botanicus, seu, Synonymia plantarum universalis, Editio secunda, Pars II. Typis et sumptibus J. E. Cottae, Tubinga, 810 pp." type="book" year="1841">Steudel 1841: 369</bibRefCitation>
). As a consequence, it is likely that 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kunth" authorityYear="1823" box="[963,1091,159,184]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Polycarpon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="apurense">
<emphasis box="[963,1091,159,184]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="107">P. apurense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is part of this group. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kunth" authorityYear="1823" box="[1323,1452,159,184]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Polycarpon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="apurense">
<emphasis box="[1323,1452,159,184]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="107">P. apurense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<emphasis box="[282,517,194,220]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="107">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1759" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1753" box="[282,455,194,220]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Polycarpon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tetraphyllum">P. tetraphyllum</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[465,517,195,220]" pageId="2" pageNumber="107" sensu="stricto">s.str.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
being more pubescent, leaves linear to lanceolate, ellipsoidal reticulate brown to reddish seeds with little spines in the dorsal margin, while 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1759" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1753" box="[810,982,230,256]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Polycarpon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="107" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tetraphyllum">
<emphasis box="[810,982,230,256]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="107">P. tetraphyllum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[991,1046,231,257]" pageId="2" pageNumber="107" sensu="stricto">
<emphasis box="[991,1039,231,256]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="107">s.str</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
is glabrous, the leaves are ovate or obovate, D-shaped papillate white to yellowish seeds unarmed in the dorsal margin.
</paragraph>
